devdoc.author: Ivan Carneiro
devdoc.details: Implements features like bid increments, automatic extensions, and refunds with commission

params._duration: The duration of the auction (in seconds).
params._initValue: The initial value of the auction item.

getWinner().details: This function can be called after the auction has ended.

makeBid().details: Requires bid value to exceed current bid by minimum increment.

returnsBids().details: Only the auction owner can call this function.

withDraw().details: Only the balance owner can call this function.
